App-SimpleScan-Plugin-LinkCheck version 0.0.1

Basic link checking for simple_scan

%% has_link "Next Page"

At least one link with the text "Next page" exists on this page.

%% has_link "Details"  == 7

Exactly 7 links named "Details" exist on this page.

%% has_link "Options" > 1

More than one link named "Options" exists on the page.

%% no_link  "Wrong"

No links named "wrong" exist on the page.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



DEPENDENCIES

None.


